=== Soundst Smart Links ===
Contributors: SoundStrategies
Donate link: None
Tags: Sound Strategies, Smart Links
Requires at least: 3.0
Tested up to: 3.4.1
Stable tag: 0.0.4

Allows you to add smart links from the Smart Links Meta box.

== Description ==

This plugin allows to add smart links from the Smart Links Meta box.

== Installation ==

1. Upload the ss-smart-links folder to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
3. Adjust the plugin settings

